title: Encore: Ellen Pompeo Doesn't Do Anything She Doesn't Want To
description:
This week Laura Brown sits down with actress and producer Ellen Pompeo to discuss privilege, power and literally not giving a f**k. She shares how she got that record-breaking raise and what’s next after 17 seasons of Grey’s Anatomy.
